page.title: 11News item 1985 (contd.)
page.content: The helcopter managed to save two and the rescue boat managed to save one person. The forth person they could not find.We waved to the man in the helicopter and suprisingly he waved backto us.The serch lasted for 7 hours. the men were said to be in their nineteens or twenties.two of the men were found climbing up the cliff and the other one was found in the water.An ambulance with a police escort came zooming to the scene.When my dad came back in he was freezing cold.The forth one has been missing for ages and is most probably missing now.So it turned out to be an exighting and tragic evening.
